Lee, who worked as a housekeeper throughout her life, was born in Mississippi in 1935 and gave birth to Winfrey when she was 18 years old.  
    
        
She and Winfrey's father, Vernon Winfrey, never married.Winfrey was initially raised by her grandmother, before joining her mother and half-siblings, Jeffrey and Patricia (both since deceased), in Milwaukee. She later moved to live with her father in Tennessee as a teenager.In 2011, Winfrey revealed on her show that her mother had given up a daughter, also named Patricia, for adoption at birth.
            

